thread.title: BRIEF-India's Dhanlaxmi Bank Dec Qtr Loss Widens

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-India's Dhanlaxmi Bank Dec Qtr Loss Widens

organizations.name: dhanlaxmi bank dec qtr loss widens feb

text:
Feb 8 (Reuters) - Dhanlaxmi Bank Ltd:
* DEC QUARTER NET LOSS 217.4 MILLION RUPEES VERSUS LOSS OF 81.8 MILLION RUPEES LAST YEAR
* DEC QUARTER INTEREST EARNED 2.48 BILLION RUPEES VERSUS 2.68 BILLION RUPEES LAST YEAR
* DEC QUARTER PROVISIONS 484.1 MILLION RUPEES VERSUS 192.3 MILLION RUPEES LAST YEAR
* DEC QUARTER GROSS NPA 6.96 PERCENT VERSUS 6.11 PERCENT PREVIOUS QUARTER
* DEC QUARTER NET NPA 4.08 PERCENT VERSUS 3.67 PERCENT PREVIOUS QUARTER Source text: bit.ly/2H07cai Further company coverage:
